---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = 'Privacy Policy — Genfy';
const description = 'How Genfy handles your data: cookies, advertising, analytics and user rights.';
---
<Layout title={title} description={description} lang="en">
  <article>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="muted">Last updated: April 26, 2026.</p>

    <p>
      This policy explains what information Genfy ("we", "the site") collects when you visit
      genfy.net, how we use it and what your rights are.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
    <p>
      Genfy is a no-signup site: we don't ask for email, name or account. Most generators
      run entirely in your browser, which means the content you enter (for example, text
      for a QR code) is not sent to our servers.
    </p>
    <p>What we automatically receive when you visit:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Basic technical data (IP address, browser type, operating system).</li>
      <li>Pages visited and time on page.</li>
      <li>Traffic source (search engine, link, direct).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. Cookies and similar technologies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies for three purposes:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Functional:</strong> remembering your preferences (e.g., language).</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> understanding which generators are most used.</li>
      <li><strong>Advertising:</strong> displaying relevant ads via Google AdSense.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Advertising — Google AdSense</h2>
    <p>
      Genfy displays ads from Google AdSense to sustain the site. Google and its partners
      may use cookies to show ads based on your visits to this and other sites. You can:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Opt out of personalized ads via <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="nofollow noopener">Google's ad settings</a>.</li>
      <li>Opt out via <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" rel="nofollow noopener">aboutads.info</a> or <a href="https://www.youronlinechoices.com" rel="nofollow noopener">youronlinechoices.com</a>.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Third parties</h2>
    <p>
      In addition to Google AdSense, we may use Google Analytics or equivalents to
      understand aggregate site usage. We do not sell or share your data with other third
      parties for marketing purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      If you reside in the EU, UK, California or another jurisdiction with similar laws,
      you have the right to request access, correction or deletion of your personal data.
      Write to <a href="mailto:privacy@genfy.net">privacy@genfy.net</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>6. Children</h2>
    <p>
      Genfy is not directed at children under 13 and we do not knowingly collect data from
      minors.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Changes</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this policy. The last update date appears at the top. Continued use of
      the site after a change implies acceptance of the current version.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
